 <a href="/go/see-guru/" target="_blank" rel="noopener sponsored nofollow" class="bg-emerald-600 text-white text-center font-bold py-3 px-8 rounded-lg hover:bg-emerald-500 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap w-full text-center">Try See Guru Free
